entries.femaleVariant: It's pissing me off. Can't get a signal on the road – don't even know if someone swiped right on me.
How 'bout someone from here, eh? I've seen Reggie checking you out – at least he's not murdery-lookin' like the others.
Ugh, I had a dog named Reggie. Then he ran away. History'll repeat itself, I can feel it...
